{"tid":2041412,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"甩開對中國依賴 英國號召民主國家組「D10」聯盟","createTime":"2020-05-29T08:26:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T10:04:28.000Z","uid":28114,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"265fc4d51695af7c7a3144ddf29b7f7d4baa7b09","tid":2041412,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T08:26:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img-ltn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/05/29/phpGelM16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-ltn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F05%2F29%2FphpGelM16.jpg&h=898c5f51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國政府正制定計畫減少對中國依賴程度。（彭博）<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕英國有感武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19）疫情期間過於依賴中國醫療、戰略物資，首相強森指示政府官員擬定對策，如今更有意推動全球10個重要民主國家，組成「D10」聯盟。<br />\n<br />\n原先有意讓中國科技大廠華為有限度加入5G建設的英國，決定減少華為參與英國基礎建設，目標要在2023年「歸零」。《路透》引述《泰晤士報》報導，作為斷開華為的替代方案，英國將尋求籌組由10個民主國家組成的「D10」聯盟。<br />\n<br />\n報導中提到，英國政府已和美國就此事聯繫，成員將以「G7」（美國、加拿大、英國、法國、德國、義大利、日本）為基礎，加上澳洲、印度和南韓。<br />\n<br />\n《泰晤士報》先前曾報導，為避免大幅仰賴從中國進口醫療、戰略物資，英國政府正在訂定加強英國國安的《防衛計畫》，由外交大臣拉布（Dominic Raab）領導。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3180749\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3180749&d=nsl8wma01YyMGEZOa9B33Apem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=0b9e01aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3180749&h=b84c88b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3180749</a>"},{"pid":"3dc51174465c8a2a454a67f2ba2c7a2e70abf6de","tid":2041412,"uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T08:27:04.000Z","msg":"英撚硬起來了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5b97fb5d5d8104477ead5f8eee202e2899aedd8","tid":2041412,"uid":165683,"like":0,"